该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - tasks (read_write): Dict mapping task_id to {title, description, status, assignee_id, project_id, priority}
  - projects (read_write): Dict mapping project_id to {name, owner, task_ids, deadline}
  - assignments (read_write): Dict mapping assignment_id to {task_id, assignee_id, assigned_at, status}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
